column6:
2 Bedroom House near Apple, The Domain and 20 minutes to downtown.
Quiet neighborhood, very good location.
Two minute walk to HEB grocery store/mall. 
Two minute drive to Apple campus. 
Five minutes from The Domain shops and restaurants.
Five minutes to access Mopac and 183 Highway. 
20 minutes to downtown area.
column9: Cute house near Apple, The Domain, and Highways.
